262
00:13:41,529 --> 00:13:42,820
for these kinds of recurrences.

263
00:13:42,820 --> 00:13:47,690
And it won't be completely
easy because it took Europeans

264
00:13:47,690 --> 00:13:51,501
six centuries to find
