1069
01:01:51,590 --> 01:01:52,090
OK?

1070
01:01:52,090 --> 01:01:58,920
So let's guess a
constant times 3 to the n

1071
01:01:58,920 --> 01:02:01,560
and see if we can
make it work, not

1072
01:02:01,560 --> 01:02:03,452
