1095
01:03:27,860 --> 01:03:36,060
equals-- c is minus 3--
minus 3 to the n plus 1.

1096
01:03:36,060 --> 01:03:36,560
All right?

1097
01:03:36,560 --> 01:03:41,370
So now I found a solution where
